high_descs: Turn around, then go left, then go right, then turn left to face the microwave.
Take the egg from the microwave.
Go left around the kitchen island, then turn right to face the sink.
Wash the egg in the sink.
Go to the counter to the right of the sink, with the plant on it.
Place the egg on the counter, to the right of the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean egg on the counter.

high_descs: Walk around the island and turn to the left to face the microwave.
Open the door to the microwave, take out an egg, and close the door.
Turn to the left , walk around the island, and turn right at the sink.
Place the egg in the sink to the right of the kettle. rinse the egg off with water, turn the water off, and take the egg out of the sink.
Move in front of the counter to the right of the sink.
Place the egg on the edge of the counter.
Turn left, then right, and then turn to face your left.
Open the microwave and pick up an egg from in it, then close the door
Turn to face the kitchen counter to the right of the sink
Rinse the egg in the sink
Move to the right of your position
Place the egg on the kitchen counter
anns.task_desc: Place a washed egg on the kitchen counter

high_descs: turn left, walk around the kitchen to the microwave
open the microwave, take the egg out of the microwave, close the microwave
turn around, walk to the sink
put the egg in the sink, wash the egg with water, take the egg out
walk to the right a little
put the egg down on the counter
anns.task_desc: take the egg out of microwave, wash the egg, put it on the counter

high_descs: Turn to the left and then the right to locate the microwave.
Open the microwave, take out the potato and shut the door.
Take the potato and go to the left around the island and find the sink.
Put the potato in the sink, turn the water on and off again. Take the potato out of the sink.
Take the potato and take a step to the right.
Place the potato on the counter, to the right of the sink.
anns.task_desc: Remove a potato from the microwave and place it on the counter.
